title: Damkutla Dumkutla Lyrics TNPL Anthem
stanzas:
Damkutla Dumkutla
udukutla adungutla
thenna matta
paricha atta
engalukku bat-tu

udukutla adungutla
sevura stump-a

moonu koda pottu

naanga nara nara
enga adi thara thara

yaaru ingae
ara kora.

udukutla adungutla

semma matter thaan
namma TNPL maappu
